# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# USDA NASS QuickStats API key  (needed ONLY to rebuild data: scripts 01, 01b)
#
# HOW TO USE:
#   1. Request a free key (instant, emailed to you):
#          https://quickstats.nass.usda.gov/api
#   2. Rename / copy this file to ".Renviron" (no .example) in this same
#      folder — the repo root.
#   3. Replace PASTE-YOUR-KEY-HERE below with your key. Keep the
#      "NASS_API_KEY=" prefix, no quotes, no spaces around the = sign.
#   4. Restart R (RStudio: Session > Restart R) so the key loads.
#
# Not rebuilding the data? You don't need this at all — the repo ships the
# computed outputs, so run_all.R renders the dashboard without a key.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
NASS_API_KEY=PASTE-YOUR-KEY-HERE
